Bookmark Your Favorite YouTube Videos With Ease

How to use:
--> Click on the blue icon near the video player controls
--> Click the extension icon to view your bookmarks

Features:
--> Create, Rename, and Delete Bookmarks
--> Minimalistic and Simple Design
